    "causal_summary": "The D5 research agent found the system already has basic empty-result handling, trace envelopes, session transition trace, token budgets, session dedup, and evidence-gap detection. The gap is not raw capability but shaping these signals into an **AI-caller-friendly DECISION CONTRACT** — structured payloads that let the calling AI make informed decisions about retries, abstention, follow-up queries, and presentation depth without parsing free-text or guessing.",
